  "content": "<h2>11 Wonderful Waze Settings Everyone Should Be Using</h2><div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><div contenteditable=\"false\" data-hidecredit=\"false\" data-imagerights=\"shutterstock\" data-syndicationrights=\"true\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-height=\"3375\" data-id=\"f49179fa0853dcc396a1ca131da25288\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommend-id=\"image://f49179fa0853dcc396a1ca131da25288\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-width=\"6000\" draggable=\"false\"><p><span><div><p><img alt=\"Image for article titled 11 Wonderful Waze Settings Everyone Should Be Using\" data-alt=\"Image for article titled 11 Wonderful Waze Settings Everyone Should Be Using\" data-anim-src=\"\" data-chomp-id=\"f49179fa0853dcc396a1ca131da25288\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fill,f_auto,fl_progressive,g_center,h_80,pg_1,q_80,w_80/f49179fa0853dcc396a1ca131da25288.jpg 80w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,g_center,pg_1,q_60,w_140/f49179fa0853dcc396a1ca131da25288.jpg 140w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,g_center,pg_1,q_60,w_265/f49179fa0853dcc396a1ca131da25288.jpg 265w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,g_center,pg_1,q_60,w_340/f49179fa0853dcc396a1ca131da25288.jpg 340w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,g_center,pg_1,q_60,w_490/f49179fa0853dcc396a1ca131da25288.jpg 490w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,g_center,pg_1,q_60,w_645/f49179fa0853dcc396a1ca131da25288.jpg 645w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,g_center,pg_1,q_60,w_740/f49179fa0853dcc396a1ca131da25288.jpg 740w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,g_center,pg_1,q_60,w_965/f49179fa0853dcc396a1ca131da25288.jpg 965w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,g_center,pg_1,q_60,w_1165/f49179fa0853dcc396a1ca131da25288.jpg 1165w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,g_center,pg_1,q_60,w_1315/f49179fa0853dcc396a1ca131da25288.jpg 1315w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,g_center,pg_1,q_60,w_1465/f49179fa0853dcc396a1ca131da25288.jpg 1465w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,g_center,pg_1,q_60,w_1600/f49179fa0853dcc396a1ca131da25288.jpg 1600w\" draggable=\"auto\" sizes=\"     (max-width: 25em) calc(100vw - 32px),     (max-width: 37.31em) calc(100vw - 32px),     (min-width: 37.37em) and (max-width: 49.94em) calc(100vw - 32px),     (min-width: 50em) and (max-width: 63.69em) 800px,     (min-width: 63.75em) and (max-width: 85.19em) calc(66.5vw - 32px),     800px    \" src=\"/calibre/LifeHacker--Wed--25-Aug-2021----/feed_0/article_13/images/img1_u8.jpg\"></p></div></span></p><div><p>Photo: Din Mohd Yaman (Shutterstock)</p></div></div><p>Google’s got the navigation app market locked down tight, owning two of the most popular navigation apps for Android and iPhone. Google Maps has lots of excellent features and is pre-loaded on Android phones sold in most places around the world, but in spite of that, Waze has a cult following in several countries, including the U.S.<br></p><p>There are lots of people who prefer Waze over Google Maps, and it’s easy to see why—it’s essentially Google Maps with personality. It also has several great features that you should check out. Here are some of the best.</p></div><div><div contenteditable=\"false\" data-hidecredit=\"false\" data-imagerights=\"shutterstock\" data-syndicationrights=\"true\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-height=\"2248\" data-id=\"f4f27515a92fd6c8b3b6e1a081c5209f\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommend-id=\"image://f4f27515a92fd6c8b3b6e1a081c5209f\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-width=\"3993\" draggable=\"false\"><p><span><div><p><img alt=\"Image for article titled 11 Wonderful Waze Settings Everyone Should Be Using\" data-alt=\"Image for article titled 11 Wonderful Waze Settings Everyone Should Be Using\" data-anim-src=\"\" data-chomp-id=\"f4f27515a92fd6c8b3b6e1a081c5209f\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fill,f_auto,fl_progressive,g_center,h_80,pg_1,q_80,w_80/f4f27515a92fd6c8b3b6e1a081c5209f.jpg 80w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,g_center,pg_1,q_60,w_140/f4f27515a92fd6c8b3b6e1a081c5209f.jpg 140w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,g_center,pg_1,q_60,w_265/f4f27515a92fd6c8b3b6e1a081c5209f.jpg 265w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,g_center,pg_1,q_60,w_340/f4f27515a92fd6c8b3b6e1a081c5209f.jpg 340w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,g_center,pg_1,q_60,w_490/f4f27515a92fd6c8b3b6e1a081c5209f.jpg 490w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,g_center,pg_1,q_60,w_645/f4f27515a92fd6c8b3b6e1a081c5209f.jpg 645w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,g_center,pg_1,q_60,w_740/f4f27515a92fd6c8b3b6e1a081c5209f.jpg 740w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,g_center,pg_1,q_60,w_965/f4f27515a92fd6c8b3b6e1a081c5209f.jpg 965w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,g_center,pg_1,q_60,w_1165/f4f27515a92fd6c8b3b6e1a081c5209f.jpg 1165w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,g_center,pg_1,q_60,w_1315/f4f27515a92fd6c8b3b6e1a081c5209f.jpg 1315w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,g_center,pg_1,q_60,w_1465/f4f27515a92fd6c8b3b6e1a081c5209f.jpg 1465w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,g_center,pg_1,q_60,w_1600/f4f27515a92fd6c8b3b6e1a081c5209f.jpg 1600w\" draggable=\"auto\" sizes=\"     (max-width: 25em) calc(100vw - 32px),     (max-width: 37.31em) calc(100vw - 32px),     (min-width: 37.37em) and (max-width: 49.94em) calc(100vw - 32px),     (min-width: 50em) and (max-width: 63.69em) 800px,     (min-width: 63.75em) and (max-width: 85.19em) calc(66.5vw - 32px),     800px    \" src=\"/calibre/LifeHacker--Wed--25-Aug-2021----/feed_0/article_13/images/img2_u1.jpg\"></p></div></span></p><div><p>Photo: Najmi Arif (Shutterstock)</p></div></div><p>Waze ships with a built-in speedometer that is extremely useful. It shows you how fast you’re going and it can alert you when you’re over or below the speed limit. (Rachel would’ve loved to have Waze in <em>Friends</em> season 7, episode 23.)<br></p><p>Open Waze and go to <strong>Settings &gt; Speedometer &gt; Show speed limit</strong> and set it to <strong>Always</strong>. This will show the speed limit on the map. Then go back to the Speedometer settings page and enable <strong>Alert when speeding</strong> for Waze to let you know when you’re above the limit.</p></div><div><div contenteditable=\"false\" data-hidecredit=\"false\" data-imagerights=\"other-license\" data-syndicationrights=\"false\" data-format=\"png\" data-height=\"900\" data-id=\"395360362604511ab955df424fb1813f\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommend-id=\"image://395360362604511ab955df424fb1813f\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-width=\"1600\" draggable=\"false\"><p><span><div><p><img alt=\"Image for article titled 11 Wonderful Waze Settings Everyone Should Be Using\" data-alt=\"Image for article titled 11 Wonderful Waze Settings Everyone Should Be Using\" data-anim-src=\"\" data-chomp-id=\"395360362604511ab955df424fb1813f\" data-format=\"png\" data-srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fill,f_auto,fl_progressive,g_center,h_80,pg_1,q_80,w_80/395360362604511ab955df424fb1813f.png 80w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,g_center,pg_1,q_60,w_140/395360362604511ab955df424fb1813f.png 140w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,g_center,pg_1,q_60,w_265/395360362604511ab955df424fb1813f.png 265w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,g_center,pg_1,q_60,w_340/395360362604511ab955df424fb1813f.png 340w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,g_center,pg_1,q_60,w_490/395360362604511ab955df424fb1813f.png 490w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,g_center,pg_1,q_60,w_645/395360362604511ab955df424fb1813f.png 645w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,g_center,pg_1,q_60,w_740/395360362604511ab955df424fb1813f.png 740w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,g_center,pg_1,q_60,w_965/395360362604511ab955df424fb1813f.png 965w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,g_center,pg_1,q_60,w_1165/395360362604511ab955df424fb1813f.png 1165w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,g_center,pg_1,q_60,w_1315/395360362604511ab955df424fb1813f.png 1315w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,g_center,pg_1,q_60,w_1465/395360362604511ab955df424fb1813f.png 1465w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,g_center,pg_1,q_60,w_1600/395360362604511ab955df424fb1813f.png 1600w\" draggable=\"auto\" sizes=\"     (max-width: 25em) calc(100vw - 32px),     (max-width: 37.31em) calc(100vw - 32px),     (min-width: 37.37em) and (max-width: 49.94em) calc(100vw - 32px),     (min-width: 50em) and (max-width: 63.69em) 800px,     (min-width: 63.75em) and (max-width: 85.19em) calc(66.5vw - 32px),     800px    \" src=\"/calibre/LifeHacker--Wed--25-Aug-2021----/feed_0/article_13/images/img3.png\"></p></div></span></p></div><p>Why keep a boring Waze voice when you’ve got so many fun options? If you’re tired of the neutral navigation assistant, go to Waze <strong>Settings &gt; Voice and sound</strong> and check your options. The English voice has many options such as&nbsp;<em>PAW Patrol</em>, <em>Boy George</em>, and Master Chief from <em>Halo</em> so you can have a good laugh while navigating to your destination.</p><p>If you’re feeling adventurous, you can even record your own voice and set it as the default on Waze. Under <strong>Voice and sound</strong> settings, tap <strong>Record new voice</strong>, and have fun.</p></div><div><div contenteditable=\"false\" data-hidecredit=\"false\" data-imagerights=\"shutterstock\" data-syndicationrights=\"true\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-height=\"3362\" data-id=\"557d280fcbfdf488194e5699c3a1512e\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommend-id=\"image://557d280fcbfdf488194e5699c3a1512e\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-width=\"5987\" draggable=\"false\"><p><span><div><p><img alt=\"Image for article titled 11 Wonderful Waze Settings Everyone Should Be Using\" data-alt=\"Image for article titled 11 Wonderful Waze Settings Everyone Should Be Using\" data-anim-src=\"\" data-chomp-id=\"557d280fcbfdf488194e5699c3a1512e\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fill,f_auto,fl_progressive,g_center,h_80,pg_1,q_80,w_80/557d280fcbfdf488194e5699c3a1512e.jpg 80w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,g_center,pg_1,q_60,w_140/557d280fcbfdf488194e5699c3a1512e.jpg 140w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,g_center,pg_1,q_60,w_265/557d280fcbfdf488194e5699c3a1512e.jpg 265w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,g_center,pg_1,q_60,w_340/557d280fcbfdf488194e5699c3a1512e.jpg 340w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,g_center,pg_1,q_60,w_490/557d280fcbfdf488194e5699c3a1512e.jpg 490w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,g_center,pg_1,q_60,w_645/557d280fcbfdf488194e5699c3a1512e.jpg 645w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,g_center,pg_1,q_60,w_740/557d280fcbfdf488194e5699c3a1512e.jpg 740w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,g_center,pg_1,q_60,w_965/557d280fcbfdf488194e5699c3a1512e.jpg 965w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,g_center,pg_1,q_60,w_1165/557d280fcbfdf488194e5699c3a1512e.jpg 1165w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,g_center,pg_1,q_60,w_1315/557d280fcbfdf488194e5699c3a1512e.jpg 1315w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,g_center,pg_1,q_60,w_1465/557d280fcbfdf488194e5699c3a1512e.jpg 1465w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,g_center,pg_1,q_60,w_1600/557d280fcbfdf488194e5699c3a1512e.jpg 1600w\" draggable=\"auto\" sizes=\"     (max-width: 25em) calc(100vw - 32px),     (max-width: 37.31em) calc(100vw - 32px),     (min-width: 37.37em) and (max-width: 49.94em) calc(100vw - 32px),     (min-width: 50em) and (max-width: 63.69em) 800px,     (min-width: 63.75em) and (max-width: 85.19em) calc(66.5vw - 32px),     800px    \" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,g_center,pg_1,q_60,w_140/557d280fcbfdf488194e5699c3a1512e.jpg\"></p></div></span></p><div><p>Photo: Mohd Syis Zulkipli (Shutterstock)</p></div></div><p>One of the things Waze doesn’t make obvious is how to find alternative routes, but that option appears before you start the trip. After you’ve set a destination, tap the <strong>Routes</strong> option and go to the <strong>Map view</strong> tab to view alternatives and choose the one that works best for you.<br></p></div><div><div contenteditable=\"false\" data-hidecredit=\"false\" data-imagerights=\"shutterstock\" data-syndicationrights=\"true\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-height=\"2805\" data-id=\"b51d0368d36c0b64874cf76513c3fd03\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommend-id=\"image://b51d0368d36c0b64874cf76513c3fd03\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-width=\"5010\" draggable=\"false\"><p><span><div><p><img alt=\"Image for article titled 11 Wonderful Waze Settings Everyone Should Be Using\" data-alt=\"Image for article titled 11 Wonderful Waze Settings Everyone Should Be Using\" data-anim-src=\"\" data-chomp-id=\"b51d0368d36c0b64874cf76513c3fd03\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fill,f_auto,fl_progressive,g_center,h_80,pg_1,q_80,w_80/b51d0368d36c0b64874cf76513c3fd03.jpg 80w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,g_center,pg_1,q_60,w_140/b51d0368d36c0b64874cf76513c3fd03.jpg 140w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,g_center,pg_1,q_60,w_265/b51d0368d36c0b64874cf76513c3fd03.jpg 265w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,g_center,pg_1,q_60,w_340/b51d0368d36c0b64874cf76513c3fd03.jpg 340w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,g_center,pg_1,q_60,w_490/b51d0368d36c0b64874cf76513c3fd03.jpg 490w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,g_center,pg_1,q_60,w_645/b51d0368d36c0b64874cf76513c3fd03.jpg 645w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,g_center,pg_1,q_60,w_740/b51d0368d36c0b64874cf76513c3fd03.jpg 740w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,g_center,pg_1,q_60,w_965/b51d0368d36c0b64874cf76513c3fd03.jpg 965w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,g_center,pg_1,q_60,w_1165/b51d0368d36c0b64874cf76513c3fd03.jpg 1165w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,g_center,pg_1,q_60,w_1315/b51d0368d36c0b64874cf76513c3fd03.jpg 1315w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,g_center,pg_1,q_60,w_1465/b51d0368d36c0b64874cf76513c3fd03.jpg 1465w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,g_center,pg_1,q_60,w_1600/b51d0368d36c0b64874cf76513c3fd03.jpg 1600w\" draggable=\"auto\" sizes=\"     (max-width: 25em) calc(100vw - 32px),     (max-width: 37.31em) calc(100vw - 32px),     (min-width: 37.37em) and (max-width: 49.94em) calc(100vw - 32px),     (min-width: 50em) and (max-width: 63.69em) 800px,     (min-width: 63.75em) and (max-width: 85.19em) calc(66.5vw - 32px),     800px    \" src=\"/calibre/LifeHacker--Wed--25-Aug-2021----/feed_0/article_13/images/img4_u2.jpg\"></p></div></span></p><div><p>Photo: David Orsoazurri (Shutterstock)</p></div></div><p>Keep using Waze for a while and you’ll begin to see trip suggestions. This is Waze finding spots you may be interested in and suggesting that you go check these out. Trip suggestions appear above the ETA bar in Waze, and you’ll be able to swipe through cards to explore these suggestions.<br></p></div><div><div contenteditable=\"false\" data-hidecredit=\"false\" data-imagerights=\"shutterstock\" data-syndicationrights=\"true\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-height=\"2153\" data-id=\"5f902260a8e3dd35e04f947442d9d697\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommend-id=\"image://5f902260a8e3dd35e04f947442d9d697\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-width=\"3839\" draggable=\"false\"><p><span><div><p><img alt=\"Image for article titled 11 Wonderful Waze Settings Everyone Should Be Using\" data-alt=\"Image for article titled 11 Wonderful Waze Settings Everyone Should Be Using\" data-anim-src=\"\" data-chomp-id=\"5f902260a8e3dd35e04f947442d9d697\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fill,f_auto,fl_progressive,g_center,h_80,pg_1,q_80,w_80/5f902260a8e3dd35e04f947442d9d697.jpg 80w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,g_center,pg_1,q_60,w_140/5f902260a8e3dd35e04f947442d9d697.jpg 140w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,g_center,pg_1,q_60,w_265/5f902260a8e3dd35e04f947442d9d697.jpg 265w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,g_center,pg_1,q_60,w_340/5f902260a8e3dd35e04f947442d9d697.jpg 340w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,g_center,pg_1,q_60,w_490/5f902260a8e3dd35e04f947442d9d697.jpg 490w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,g_center,pg_1,q_60,w_645/5f902260a8e3dd35e04f947442d9d697.jpg 645w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,g_center,pg_1,q_60,w_740/5f902260a8e3dd35e04f947442d9d697.jpg 740w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,g_center,pg_1,q_60,w_965/5f902260a8e3dd35e04f947442d9d697.jpg 965w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,g_center,pg_1,q_60,w_1165/5f902260a8e3dd35e04f947442d9d697.jpg 1165w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,g_center,pg_1,q_60,w_1315/5f902260a8e3dd35e04f947442d9d697.jpg 1315w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,g_center,pg_1,q_60,w_1465/5f902260a8e3dd35e04f947442d9d697.jpg 1465w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,g_center,pg_1,q_60,w_1600/5f902260a8e3dd35e04f947442d9d697.jpg 1600w\" draggable=\"auto\" sizes=\"     (max-width: 25em) calc(100vw - 32px),     (max-width: 37.31em) calc(100vw - 32px),     (min-width: 37.37em) and (max-width: 49.94em) calc(100vw - 32px),     (min-width: 50em) and (max-width: 63.69em) 800px,     (min-width: 63.75em) and (max-width: 85.19em) calc(66.5vw - 32px),     800px    \" src=\"/calibre/LifeHacker--Wed--25-Aug-2021----/feed_0/article_13/images/img5_u3.jpg\"></p></div></span></p><div><p>Photo: dennizn (Shutterstock)</p></div></div><p>When you’re using Waze, an orange icon will appear on the map. This is the <strong>Report</strong> button, which you can use to report any errors or hazards to others who use the app. Before you start your trip, you can look up community reports to see if there are any unexpected delays on the route.<br></p></div><div><div contenteditable=\"false\" data-hidecredit=\"false\" data-imagerights=\"shutterstock\" data-syndicationrights=\"true\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-height=\"3375\" data-id=\"681dbabb3286e9a8d070cfd0161cdc78\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommend-id=\"image://681dbabb3286e9a8d070cfd0161cdc78\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-width=\"6000\" draggable=\"false\"><p><span><div><p><img alt=\"Image for article titled 11 Wonderful Waze Settings Everyone Should Be Using\" data-alt=\"Image for article titled 11 Wonderful Waze Settings Everyone Should Be Using\" data-anim-src=\"\" data-chomp-id=\"681